trans-unit.source: Defines an attribute that specifies the scope where a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" /> object should be applied when a resource is located.
trans-unit.target: Define un atributo que especifica el ámbito en el que debe aplicarse un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" /> cuando se ubica un recurso.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> class parses and generates code during compilation for a resource that has a specific file.
trans-unit.target: La <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> clase analiza y genera el código durante la compilación de un recurso que tiene un archivo específico.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> attribute defines the location scope for which the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> object will be called.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> atributo define el ámbito de ubicación para que la <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> se llamará a objeto.

trans-unit.source: By setting the <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> attribute, you can limit a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> object to certain [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] directories, such as App_Code.
trans-unit.target: Estableciendo la <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> atributo, puede limitar un <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> objeto a determinados [!INCLUDE[vstecasp](~/includes/vstecasp-md.md)] directorios, como App_Code.

trans-unit.source: If you do not apply a <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> attribute to a <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> class, by default, the attribute targets all directories.
trans-unit.target: Si no se aplica un <xref:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute> atributo a un <xref:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider> (clase), de forma predeterminada, el atributo tiene como destino todos los directorios.

trans-unit.source: The target directory that a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" /> object applies to.
trans-unit.target: Directorio de destino al que se aplica un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.Compilation.FolderLevelBuildProviderAppliesToAttribute" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the target directory that a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" /> object applies to.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene o establece el directorio de destino al que se aplica un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" />.

trans-unit.source: The directory that a <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" /> object applies to.
trans-unit.target: El directorio al que se aplica un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Configuration.FolderLevelBuildProvider" />.
